{"tid":38580,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加暗示大肆增兵：一月我會好忙","createTime":"2016-12-14T04:25:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T16:11:33.000Z","uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c8c1de652650fc5ac93e091f7780742a45fdf875","tid":38580,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:25:54.000Z","msg":"阿仙奴領隊雲加表示，他希望在一月引入能增強球隊實力的球員，但他認為這是艱巨的任務。 <br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴本季成績不佳，雲加也相信與球員實力有關，因此一向謹慎的他決定在一月收購球員。不過教授認為真正有質素的球員很難買到，而能夠買到的球員不一定能提升球隊實力。 <br />\n<br />\n雲加接受採訪時說：「<span style=\"color: red;\">沒錯，一月我將很忙，我不會透露心儀球員的名字，你們媒體自己有辦法找到答案。我們有打入歐聯的實力，但我們也很希望增強實力，不過你很難在能夠購買的球員中，找到能提升我們實力的球員。</span>沒錯，你希望找到能即買即用的球員，這就是困難的地方。雲佩斯雖然已經29歲，但曼聯花了2400萬鎊簽下他。」 <br />\n<br />\n雲加又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc56316f952f035a66b32806ffad9d7c0fd12dd4","tid":38580,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:30:26.000Z","msg":"一月買幻幻打英超，主力就打歐聯，後備兵是但落場踢下本土杯賽，電叻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e2492de433cdc9f12ea5196d3d9b49a829a003","tid":38580,"uid":39436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:30:58.000Z","msg":"忙住賣人"},{"pid":"7967bc0f1ce570ca217fb74c667b01bfdf24f6d7","tid":38580,"uid":33441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:32:00.000Z","msg":"佢老母最忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c5aa1124f103acd81f2ee9f3b326fd124ea1d40","tid":38580,"uid":44473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T04:32:24.000Z","msg":"舊聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"674934df4355465d29de468a8114e336f45ba07f","tid":38580,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"